2001-09-07  Paul Eggert  <eggert@twinsun.com>

        * io.c (redirect): When deciding to use the fdopen bug hack,
          use "__sun" rather than "solaris".  No compilers predefine
          "solaris", but both GCC and Sun C predefine "__sun".

