	* missing_d/mktime.c: likewise.

	* random.c: reorder include directives to get gawk config info
	  from random.h sooner.
	  [fcntl.h]: guard #include with HAVE_FCNTL_H test.
	  [unistd.h]: guard #include with HAVE_UNISTD_H test.

